OL,6,FThere are no plans to address a
OL,7,Fnationwide deficiency in the provision
OL,8,Fof specialist hospital units and beds
OL,9,Ffor patients with severe chronic
OL,10,Ffatigue syndrome, a senior doctor told
OL,11,Fan inquest.
OL,13,FDr Anthony Hemsley said he believed
OL,14,FNHS England was not carrying out "any
OL,15,Factive work on this at the current
OL,16,Ftime" to address the issue following
OL,17,Fthe death of Maeve Boothby-O'Neill, 27.
