OL,6,FMiss Boothby-O'Neill had been
OL,7,Fsuffering from fatigue since the age
OL,8,Fof 13, which got worse after she
OL,9,Fcompleted her A-levels.
OL,11,FLast month Deborah Archer, an
OL,12,Fassistant coroner for Devon, Plymouth
OL,13,Fand Torbay, concluded she had died
OL,14,Ffrom natural causes "because of severe
OL,15,Fmyalgic encephalomyelitis (ME)" but
OL,16,Fadjourned the hearing to consider
OL,17,Fwhether she should make a preventing
OL,18,Ffuture deaths report.
