OL,6,FResuming the inquest, the coroner
OL,7,Fheard evidence from Dr Hemsley, who is
OL,8,Fthe medical director for the Royal
OL,9,FDevon University Healthcare NHS
OL,10,FFoundation Trust.
OL,12,FHe told the inquest the trust had not
OL,13,Fbeen commissioned to provide a
OL,14,Fspecialist ME service for patients
OL,15,Fwith a severe form of the illness
OL,16,Feither before or after Miss Boothby-
OL,17,FO'Neill's death.
OL,19,F"I can be very clear," he said.
