OL,6,F"There are no such care pathways for
OL,7,Fsevere and very severe chronic fatigue
OL,8,Fsyndrome at the Royal Devon.
OL,10,F"Neither is there any physical
OL,11,Flocation to care for patients in that
OL,12,Fway specifically within a hospital
OL,13,Fsetting.
OL,15,F"The recommended physical requirements
OL,16,Fare beyond reasonable for a standard
OL,17,Fsecondary care acute hospital.
