OL,6,F"My understanding is that having
OL,7,Finvestigated matters there is no such
OL,8,Fadmissions unit or bed within Devon or
OL,9,Fthe south west region or nationally."
OL,11,FHe added: "There are essentially no
OL,12,Funits or inpatient beds in any NHS
OL,13,Finstitution, or available privately.
OL,15,F"It is certainly not within my gift to
OL,16,Fprovide that level of service."
OL,18,FThe hearing heard there were no plans
OL,19,Fto commission a service locally in
OL,20,FDevon or nationally either.
