OL,6,F"I then spoke and met with Dr Michael
OL,7,FMarsh, who is the medical director for
OL,8,FNHS England south west region, and he
OL,9,Fwas aware of the gap in service and
OL,10,Ftook my concerns very seriously," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"We decided that it would be prudent
OL,14,Ffor me to investigate the possibility
OL,15,Fof specialist commissioning.
OL,17,F"So that's a different body that
OL,18,Fprovides commissioning for this sort
OL,19,Fof level of service, which would be
OL,20,Fvery much tertiary or national.
