OL,6,F"This wasn't deemed to be appropriate
OL,7,Ffor specialist commissioning.
OL,9,F"I had a further discussion with Dr
OL,10,FMarsh and has specifically raised this
OL,11,Fissue for severe and very severe
OL,12,Fchronic fatigue syndrome patients with
OL,13,FProfessor Stephen Powis, the national
OL,14,Fmedical director of NHS England.
OL,16,F"The outcome of that is to note the
OL,17,Fdeficiency in service but Dr Marsh
OL,18,Fdidn't believe that there's any active
OL,19,Fwork on this at the current time.
