OL,10,FBoothby-O'Neill and a journalist for
OL,11,FThe Times newspaper, asked Dr Hemsley
OL,12,Fwhether he was "disappointed" by that
OL,13,Fresponse.
OL,15,F"I am not surprised that I have been
OL,16,Frequired to try different avenues to
OL,17,Fraise the profile of the question and
OL,18,Fstimulate movement in service
OL,19,Fprovision," he replied.
