OL,7,Fharrowing process and I also
OL,8,Funderstand that at the end of the
OL,9,Finquest process no one goes away
OL,10,Fhaving all the answers they want or
OL,11,Fcompletely happy.
OL,13,F"I hope by making this report it will
OL,14,Fgo some way to starting change on this
OL,15,Fimportant area."
OL,17,FIn a statement issued afterwards,
OL,18,FAndrew Gwynne, minister for public
OL,19,Fhealth and prevention, said: "My
OL,20,Fdeepest sympathies go out to Maeve's
OL,21,Ffamily and friends in this tragic case.
